nk the category of =E2=80=9CCEOs mad about short sellers=E2=80=9D is probab=
ly broad enough to encompass the=C2=A0absolute spy thriller that former Ove=
rstock.com CEO Patrick Byrne wrote at the end of his tenure in 2019, includ=
