onventional wisdom that government officials have an incentive to be nice t=
o big companies =E2=80=94=C2=A0to take a light hand in regulating them, etc=
. =E2=80=94=C2=A0so that later, when they leave government, the officials c=
an get lucrative jobs at the companies they befriended while in office.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But in fact,=C2=A0the opposite often seems to =
be true. Government officials also have powerful incentives to be=C2=A0<em>=
mean=C2=A0</em>to big companies, so that later, when they leave government,=
 they can get lucrative jobs at the companies that they=C2=A0<em>pestered=
=C2=A0</em>while in office. If you develop a reputation in government for b=
eing Tough On Industry X, that makes it=C2=A0<em>more=C2=A0</em>likely that=
 some firm in Industry X will want to hire you:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Toughness, generally, is a business v=
irtue; they will be impressed by your work ethic and creativity.</li>=09<li=
 style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">If they can offer you a nice pay package to=
=C2=A0<em>quit=C2=A0</em>the government and go work for them, then that rem=
oves you as a tough antagonist.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">If=
 you work for them, your arguments will carry more weight with other govern=
ment officials, because they will remember you as a tough regulator of Indu=
stry X.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But there are sometimes=C2=A0more direct incen=
tives. Federal prosecutors regularly reach settlements with big companies t=
hat require those companies to hire expensive compliance monitors; those lu=
crative monitoring jobs tend to go to former federal prosecutors. The SEC h=
as a whistleblower program that pays big awards to whistleblowers=C2=A0<em>=
and their lawyers</em>; the lawyers who are best able to navigate that prog=
ram and get the awards are ones who used to <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bl=
oombergbusiness.com/click/34684872.258367/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvb=
